{"tid":1279849,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[神秘學]海地巫毒咀咒[附youtube link]","createTime":"2019-07-02T18:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T08:17:32.000Z","uid":257767,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"24518378f1dd1bad48b51a7f59b3944b3f0f9c19","tid":1279849,"uid":257767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:57:42.000Z","msg":"個個po 都講政治真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同一個研究神秘學既朋友講起南美一帶既巫毒（hoodoo）傳統，其中有一種叫war-water的咀咒，令敵人既生活陷入混亂同痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n原來步驟非常簡單，只需要極常見既材料，同埋每日少少時間。<br />\n<br />\n佢叫我睇呢條youtube 片，基本上係非常詳盡：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XSO4AWgpIDk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXSO4AWgpIDk&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcxx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=bf4e0117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XSO4AWgpIDk</a> <br />\n<br />\n朋友話，呢種咀咒基本上不涉及神靈，而係將施術者既意圖放大，投射去外面等世界。<br />\n<br />\n朋友又話，呢種咀咒雖然簡單有效，又唔犯法，不過都唔建議亂試，大家睇下就好喇。<br />\n<br />\n朋友又話，唔明不妨留言，大家作學術研究。<br />\n<br />\n(而一d 吸引愛情同財富既巫術，其實都係同樣原理，只不過用既材料唔同，有興趣既話自己上youtube 搵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"71477e75cb27b2737958646cc26dee194d62c875","tid":1279849,"uid":257767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:03:31.000Z","msg":"朋友又話，無論做咩類型既魔法都好，事前事後都要沖涼，換套乾淨衫。最好在水中加少少鹽，去除負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159c550df604d7ed9b4bda6c79bd3a45549fc327","tid":1279849,"uid":257767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:20:28.000Z","msg":"朋友又話，世上根本無分黑／白魔法，只有分你既意圖／目的是否正當。"},{"pid":"8895f88047b92006e39210a1234f8ad37dc78aa3","tid":1279849,"uid":257767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}